    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>This post is part of an ongoing series about robots, past and present.  See <a href="/robot-egyptologists/">Robot Egyptologists</a>.</p>

<p>Robot quadcopters playing the James Bond theme tune.</p>

<p><iframe width="640" height="390" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/_sUeGC-8dyk " frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe></p>

<p>There is no human controlling the robots. Each one has been assigned a series of points in space that it must reach at specific times.  The robots are aware of each other and avoid collisions.</p>

